name: OPT
description:
in or out?
click to interact.

at a time when many are becoming resolved to do this and not that i like to remember that any time is a sufficient time to make a choice. often the simplest decisions are not only the easiest to make but also the most meaningful.

complicated plans are easily thwarted.
simplify.
accomplish more by thinking less.
be guided by what you feel and not by what you see.

reject the one and accept the other.
opt out of this and opt in to that.

~inspired by lao tzu~
